Release        : 6.7
Date           : 27-Nov-2003
ChangeOrder    : PRSF00077887
Title          : Add TAP3 changes.
Description    : Propagated from 6.5_SP1_EBF.
  Added new iRules to raise EDR errors if:
    - Mandatory fields have been flagged as MISSING by the inGrammar.
    - Values of fields are outside ranges specified in the TAP standard.
  Added three new iScripts to:
    - Perform field and cross-field validations on header and trailer records.
    - Perform field and cross-field validations on detail records.
    - Split the "big" EDR created by the InGrammer into one EDR per basic service.

